  <brief_title>Active Versus Non Active Drainage for the Treatment of Infected Intra-abdominal Collection</brief_title>
  <official_title>Active Versus Non Active Drainage for the Treatment of Infected Intra-abdominal Collection: a Randomized Prospective Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
