    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Infected intra-abdominal collection requiring a percutaneous drainage after surgery or
             due to a primary intra-abdominal infectious disease (e.g. diverticulitis,
             appendicitis)

          -  age over 18 years old

          -  intra-abdominal collections &gt;5 cm in diameter with signs of infections on imaging

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  pregnancy

          -  age&lt; 18 years

          -  signs of peritonitis

          -  Intensive care unit patients
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
